---
import { ShieldCheck, Heart } from "lucide-astro";
---

<section id="metodo" class="py-24 bg-background overflow-hidden scroll-mt-20">
	<div class="container mx-auto px-6">
		<div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-16">
			<div id="about-image" class="lg:w-1/2 relative opacity-0 -translate-x-20">
				<div class="absolute -top-10 -left-10 w-40 h-40 bg-primary/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
				<div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
					<img src="/images/interior_blinds.png" alt="Showroom Le Tende ad Arte - Tende da interno e artigianato ad Abbiategrasso" class="w-full h-full object-cover aspect-[4/5] hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" />
				</div>
				<div id="about-badge" class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 bg-white dark:bg-card p-6 rounded-xl shadow-xl border border-border max-w-[200px] opacity-0 scale-50">
					<div class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-1 italic">50+</div>
					<div class="text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-widest leading-tight">Anni di Esperienza Artigianale</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div id="about-content" class="lg:w-1/2 opacity-0 translate-x-20">
				<div class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-primary/5 px-4 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-primary mb-6">
					La Nostra Storia
				</div>
				<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-8 font-heading leading-tight">Artigianalità, Passione e <span class="text-primary italic">Tradizione.</span></h2>
				
				<p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground mb-10 leading-relaxed">
					Da oltre cinquant’anni realizziamo tende su misura e rivestimenti per divani con un approccio artigianale fondato su precisione, qualità dei materiali e attenzione al dettaglio. 
				</p>
				
				<div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-10">
					<div class="flex gap-4">
						<div class="h-10 w-10 shrink-0 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary">
							<ShieldCheck class="h-6 w-6" />
						</div>
						<div>
							<h4 class="font-bold mb-1">Qualità Garantita</h4>
							<p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Materiali selezionati dai migliori fornitori italiani.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="flex gap-4">
						<div class="h-10 w-10 shrink-0 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary">
							<Heart class="h-6 w-6" />
						</div>
						<div>
							<h4 class="font-bold mb-1">Cura del Dettaglio</h4>
							<p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Ogni cucitura è eseguita con precisione millimetrica.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
					Ogni progetto viene seguito con competenza e cura, per offrire soluzioni eleganti, funzionali e pensate per durare nel tempo. Dal sopralluogo gratuito alla posa in opera, siamo al tuo fianco.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<script>
	import { gsap } from "gsap";
	import { ScrollTrigger } from "gsap/ScrollTrigger";
	gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger);

	document.addEventListener("astro:page-load", () => {
		if (!document.getElementById("metodo")) return;

		// Image animation
		gsap.to("#about-image", {
			scrollTrigger: {
				trigger: "#metodo",
				start: "top 80%",
				toggleActions: "play none none none",
			},
			opacity: 1,
			x: 0,
			duration: 1.2,
			ease: "power3.out",
		});

		// Badge animation (delayed)
		gsap.to("#about-badge", {
			scrollTrigger: {
				trigger: "#metodo",
				start: "top 70%",
				toggleActions: "play none none none",
			},
			opacity: 1,
			scale: 1,
			delay: 0.6,
			duration: 1,
			ease: "back.out(1.7)",
		});

		// Content animation
		gsap.to("#about-content", {
			scrollTrigger: {
				trigger: "#metodo",
				start: "top 80%",
				toggleActions: "play none none none",
			},
			opacity: 1,
			x: 0,
			duration: 1.2,
			ease: "power3.out",
		});
	});
</script>
